Class AVLTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • AVLTree
  • public class AVLTree
extends java.lang.Object
    AVLTree class takes in given datetime, power and voltage and stores it in an AVL Tree where the data can later be searched for/retrieved using the functions of the AVLTree
